      "content": "that's a good start. can you make it a bit more descriptive about the actual people he's seeing and why he thinks they're so far behind? like, focus on the contrast between their \"primitive\" lifestyle and the \"sophistication\" of the British empire. maybe mention how they lack real law or structure and how that's why they need British guidance.",
